cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.MM

This paper is primarily focused on computer vision tasks, specifically dense tracking and video object segmentation. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also discusses the use of self-supervised learning and memory components, which are common topics in machine learning and artificial intelligence, making cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) likely sub-categories as well. The paper also involves robotics and motion tracking, which could fall under cs.RO (Robotics) and cs.MM (Multimedia).
